'''LightDM'''的目標是創造一個輕量、快速、具擴充性以及多桌面環境的[[X顯示管理器|X顯示管理器]]<ref name="Homepage">{{citation |url = http://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/LightDM |title = The Light Display Manager (LightDM) |accessdate = 17 May 2011 |archive-date = 2021-02-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210204132126/https://www.freedesktop.org/wiki/Software/LightDM/ |dead-url = no }}</ref>。它使用了很多不同的被稱作Greeters的[[前端和後端|前端]]來渲染出登入畫面<ref name="digitizor">{{citation |title = Ubuntu 11.10 To Switch From GDM To LightDM |url = http://digitizor.com/2011/05/12/ubuntu-11-10-lightdm/ |date = 12 May 2011 |accessdate = 18 May 2011 |archive-date = 2015-09-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150910151026/http://digitizor.com/2011/05/12/ubuntu-11-10-lightdm/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |last=Fischer |first=Matt |url=http://www.mattfischer.com/blog/?p=5 |title=» So You Want to Write a LightDM Greeter… Matt Fischer's Blog |publisher=Mattfischer.com |date=2012-02-07 |accessdate=2013-05-29 |archive-date=2013-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130719131630/http://www.mattfischer.com/blog/?p=5 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 特性 ==
LightDM包含了以下這些特性：
* 減少外部依賴的代碼庫
* 符合PAM、ConsoleKit等標準
* 在顯示伺服器及使用者介面間有良好的定義
* 跨桌面環境（可以用任何[[部件工具箱|部件工具箱]]編寫）
* 可在多種[[圖形使用者介面|圖形使用者介面]]下使用的良好定義[[API|API]]
* 在適當的情況及有適合的外掛的情況下，支援所有的顯示管理器

LightDM提供了至少與[[GNOME顯示管理器|GNOME顯示管理器]]一樣的功能，但它卻有一個更簡單的代碼庫，並且在運行時不需載入任何[[GNOME|GNOME]]的[[函式庫|函式庫]]<ref>{{citation |url=http://www.geek.com/articles/chips/ubuntu-adopts-lightdm-login-screens-to-get-more-exciting-20110512/ |title=Ubuntu adopts LightDM, login screens to get more exciting |publisher=Geek.com |date=12 May 2011 |accessdate=18 May 2011 |archive-date=2012-08-15 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/69wjpdbKu?url=http://www.geek.com/articles/chips/ubuntu-adopts-lightdm-login-screens-to-get-more-exciting-20110512/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。LightDM是自[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]]11.10釋出後，[[Ubuntu|Ubuntu]]、[[Edubuntu|Edubuntu]]、[[Xubuntu|Xubuntu]]以及[[Mythbuntu|Mythbuntu]]的預設顯示管理器<ref>{{citation |url=https://wiki.ubuntu.com/OneiricOcelot/ReleaseNotes |title=Ubuntu 11.10 ReleaseNotes |publisher=Canonical |accessdate=28 May 2012 |archive-date=2011-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111223145418/https://wiki.ubuntu.com/OneiricOcelot/ReleaseNotes |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Xubuntu">{{cite web|title=Xubuntu 11.10 Release Notes|url=https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Xubuntu/ReleaseNotes/OneiricOcelot/Final/|publisher=Canonical|accessdate=17 December 2012|archive-date=2013-10-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131002202219/https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Xubuntu/ReleaseNotes/OneiricOcelot/Final/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[Lubuntu|Lubuntu]]則是在12.04釋出後才將LightDM作為預設顯示管理器<ref name="Lubuntu">{{citation |url=https://wiki.ubuntu.com/PrecisePangolin/ReleaseNotes/Lubuntu |title=Lubuntu 12.04 ReleaseNotes |publisher=Canonical |accessdate=14 Jun 2012 |archive-date=2012-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120514005743/https://wiki.ubuntu.com/PrecisePangolin/ReleaseNotes/Lubuntu |dead-url=no }}</ref>，[[Kubuntu|Kubuntu]]則是從12.10才將LightDM作為預設顯示管理器<ref name="Kubuntu default">{{cite web |url=https://mail.kde.org/pipermail/plasma-devel/2012-August/020995.html |title=[RFC] Merging LightDM into KDE Workspaces |publisher=Mail.kde.org |date= |accessdate=2013-05-29 |archive-date=2015-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714160847/https://mail.kde.org/pipermail/plasma-devel/2012-August/020995.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

